culation is this... if you hand the sword, green scale, red scale and white scale to this gnome, he wil give you the reward of the Throneblade (not rusted) which would proc an enormous lifetap.<br><br>Noone to me knowledge has done the hand in, as they don't want to loose the scales I guess.  I have often thought about it though.<br><br>So that's about it.<br><br>NB.  If you did hand in the items to the gnome and you got nothing in return, could you slay the gnome and get your items back? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udenuvien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Denuvien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 6:37:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rusted Throneblade from Nortlav</span><hr size=1> Bards have done everything imaginable with that throneblade.<br>When you hadn it to him, he just says thank you, just like any other random item.<br>Pretty sure it's all just back story for an extra red scale source. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unightgod.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NightGod</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 7:21:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rusted Throneblade from Nortlav</span><hr size=1> When you kill him, you get no faction hit AND you get your sword back...not that I'd know &lt;koff&gt;. The fact that he doesn't eat it leads me to belive that its not quest related... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukezlar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kezlar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 8:57:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rusted Throneblade from Nortlav</span><hr size=1> When I handed in the burnished staff in for the VP key quest, I killed the Iks NPC after getting the medallion and was able to loot the staff back.  So just because you can loot aftre slaying the NPC doesn't have anything to do with quest or non quest NPC's.<br><br>You say that bards have tried everything, I wonder if they tried handing the sword with red/white/green scales.  I bet they didn't.<br><br>I would love to know if someone tries doing that. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uglulayenevernight.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glulayen Evernight</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/02 2:04:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=