pan><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/02 9:04:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> !</span><hr size=1> Nortlav = Valtron...but BACKWARDS!!!<br><br>Maybe if you turn in a Valtron's neck from Vulak and the Thorneblade to the gnome you get the key to the teleport firepots that have been locked since release!!<br><br>(Makes more sense he is just a way for 50-60 crowd to get scales since the dragon change. Wish he was there when I was doing the pally epic) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uodiussilvertongue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>OdiusSilvertongue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/02 12:54:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: !</span><hr size=1> Turning in all 3 scales (red/white/green) with the thorneblade wouldn't be any sort of risk at all to be honest.  Since the items are not no drop after you gave him all the items you could simply kill him (the gnome) and reloot the scales.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cingin>Cingin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/02 5:31:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: !</span><hr size=1> Sword doesn't proc the lifetap, Nortlav procs that lifetap.  Just like Sontalak procs a Dispel, and many other mobs proc many other spells.<br><br>Venril Sathir procs the same thing. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulewterpitt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LEWTERPITT</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.socal.rr.com/moshpitt/shadowdevils/images/pics/inmybelly-.gif width=50 height=30" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/02 9:57:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: !</span><hr size=1> Kezlar  :<br><br>If a mob is givens an item that is related to it (i.e. a quest item), it will automatically eat the item.<br>There isnt much risk giving him the scales, if he eats it (even after you kill him and check bod) then you know its items that are related to that npc.<br>Now...to find ~200k to get white, green and red scales. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4491.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4491.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4491.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=4491.topic><